ency values seems sufficient for a DAG implementation.\n\nThe implementation collects all nodes by gathering both the Map keys and any nodes that appear as neighbors, then performs a depth-first search with cycle detection using a recursion stack. Each node gets visited once, with neighbors explored recursively before adding the node to the sorted result, which is then reversed to produce the correct topological order.",
